About Florilow
The setting is rural with many beautiful oak trees and a small pond in Bushnell, Florida. It was purchased in 1984 by a group called the Loners on Wheels™ (LOWs) for the purpose of making it an RV community for singles 55+.  While it’s no longer owned and or managed by LOWs, its main purpose still exists for being a community for SINGLES 55+. We welcome singles of any travel club and it has become a popular meeting place for many singles who spend their winters in Florida.
